<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Stands of <i>Lolium perenne </i>in upland sites readily burn at high fire frequencies. Perennial plants are top-killed and sprout quickly from the tillers after fires (Carey 1995c, Sullivan 1992b).</div>
